vapor confirmed at 1.6 ppm, 1.6 ppm, NE wind vector directly toward Riverside 
Tower (300m). **Manifests still unavailable; chemical ID pending.**
   - Metro Overpass: Spalling contained; no collapse risk; stable for 
engineering certification path.

3. **Hazmat Escalation:** Instantiated hazmat coordinator for North Warehouse; 
